# OnePortal Frontend Rules

## File Locations

| Concern | Location |
|---------|----------|
| API functions | `src/api/<domain>Api.ts` |
| Types / interfaces | `src/types/<domain>.ts` |
| Pages | `src/pages/<Name>Page.tsx` |
| Routes | `src/App.tsx` inside `<ProtectedRoute>` / `<AppLayout>` |

## Data Fetching

```ts
// TanStack Query v5 — always wrap queryFn in arrow function
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ['sheet', projectId],
  queryFn: () => getSheetByProject(projectId!),
  enabled: !!projectId,
  retry: false,          // use retry:false for queries expected to 404
});

// Mutations
const mut = useMutation({
  mutationFn: updateRow,
  onSuccess: () => queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['sheet', projectId] }),
  onError: (err: Error) => alert(err.message),
});
```

- Always invalidate queries after mutations to keep the UI in sync

## Role Checks

```ts
const myMembership = project?.members.find(m => m.userId === currentUser?.id);
const isOwner = myMembership?.role === 'OWNER';
const isTesterOrOwner = isOwner || myMembership?.role === 'TESTER';
const isAdmin = currentUser?.role === 'ADMIN';
```

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS only — no CSS files, no inline `style={}` (exception: dynamic chart fill colours)
- Brand colour: indigo (`indigo-600` primary, `indigo-100` light background)
- Card pattern: `bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm p-4`
- Primary button: `bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg`
- Danger button: `bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg`
- Warning/replace button: `bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 border border-amber-300 hover:bg-amber-100`
- Loading spinner: `animate-spin` SVG circle/path pattern

## Charts (Recharts)

- `PieChart` for status distributions; `BarChart` (stacked) for assignment overviews
- Always wrap in `<ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height={260}>`
- Write custom tooltip components above the page function, not as inline lambdas
- Use a `STATUS_CHART_COLORS` record (`Record<RowStatus | 'null', string>`) — never hardcode hex colours inline:
  `NOT_STARTED`→`#94a3b8`, `IN_PROGRESS`→`#3b82f6`, `PASSED`→`#22c55e`, `FAILED`→`#ef4444`, `BLOCKED`→`#f97316`

## Pagination

- Use `getPaginationRange(current, total)` helper (see `ProjectTestCasesPage.tsx`)
- Offer page-size selector: options `[10, 25, 50, 100]`

## Confirmation Modals

- Use inline overlay pattern — no separate modal component
- State: `const [deleteConfirmItem, setDeleteConfirmItem] = useState<T | null>(null)`
- Show only when `deleteConfirmItem !== null`

## Icons

Lucide React only:
```ts
import { Trash2, Plus, Upload, Download, ChevronLeft } from 'lucide-react';
```
